OL,3,CThames Water funding woes deepen after
OL,4,Cshareholders pull investment plan
OL,6,FTroubled utility Thames Water has said
OL,7,Fits shareholders will not be injecting
OL,8,Fthe first #500 million of funding that
OL,9,Fwas agreed last summer into the group
OL,10,Fas industry regulations make its
OL,11,Fbusiness plan "uninvestible".
OL,13,FThames Water said the funding plan
OL,14,Fdrawn up last July was subject to
OL,15,Fconditions, including a business plan
OL,16,Fthat is supported by "appropriate
OL,17,Fregulatory arrangements".
