OL,3,CThames Water funding woes deepen after
OL,4,Cshareholders pull investment plan
OL,6,FIt said the regulations being imposed
OL,7,Fby industry watchdog Ofwat "make the
OL,8,FPR24 plan "uninvestible", and as a
OL,9,Fresult the shareholder support letter
OL,10,Ffrom last July "has not been
OL,11,Fsatisfied".
OL,13,F"The first #500 million of the new
OL,14,Fequity that had been anticipated will
OL,15,Fnot be provided by Thames Water's
OL,16,Fshareholders by 31 March 2024," it
OL,17,Frevealed.
