OL,3,CThames Water funding woes deepen after
OL,4,Cshareholders pull investment plan
OL,6,FThames Water said it was in ongoing
OL,7,Ftalks with industry regulator Ofwat to
OL,8,Fsecure regulations that are
OL,9,F"affordable for customers, deliverable
OL,10,Fand financeable for Thames Water, as
OL,11,Fwell as investible for equity
OL,12,Finvestors".
OL,14,FIt comes after months of talks
OL,15,Finvolving the government and
OL,16,Fregulators surrounding the company's
OL,17,Ffinancial situation.
