OL,3,CThames Water funding woes deepen after
OL,4,Cshareholders pull investment plan
OL,6,FThe firm said once the new regulatory
OL,7,Fplan is agreed with Ofwat, it "intends
OL,8,Fto pursue all options to secure the
OL,9,Frequired equity investment from new or
OL,10,Fexisting shareholders".
OL,12,FLast July, it agreed a rescue funding
OL,13,Fplan with shareholders ` including the
OL,14,FUniversities Superannuation Scheme
OL,15,F(USS), China's sovereign wealth fund,
OL,16,Fa Canadian pension fund and the BT
OL,17,FPension Scheme ` that would see them
OL,18,Fpump in #750 million, with the first
OL,19,F#500 million due by the end of this
OL,20,Fmonth.
